
Instructions:

Start with example4
1) Add two functions: static void initdouble(double *input) 
and static void mindouble(double *output, const double *input)
2) Create a new hpx_lco_reduce_new; call it newdt; make it of size double and make it have nDoms inputs.  Initialize it with initdouble and make the reduction operation mindouble.
3) Add newdt to the Domain structure; initialize newdt in initDomain
4) In advanceDomain, perform an allreduce every timestep
